line_1: Blackens the morn to grace his obsequies.
line_2: Untimely darkness gathering round the skies,

line_1: And every God to Join in th' Obsequies,
line_2: Call'd all my Sisters with my frantick Cries,

line_1: And every God to Join in th' Obsequies,
line_2: With Tears made Helycon brackish as the Seas.
